Union, Intersect and Minus(Set operations)
1. Find the ids of sailors who have reserved a red boat or a green boat
2. Find the names of sailors who have reserved boat 102.
3. Find the name and the age of the youngest sailor
4. Find the names of sailors who have reserved all boats

Query
 1. select sid from reserves where bid in (select bid from boats where color='red')
    union
    select sid from reserves where bid in (select bid from boats where color='green');

2. select sname from sailors where sid in (select sid from reserves)
   intersect
   select sname from sailors where sid in(select sid from reserves where bid=102);

3.select sname,age from sailors
 intersect
 select sname,age from sailors where age = (select min(age) from sailors);

 4. select distinct sname from sailors where sid in (select sid from reserves intersect select sid from sailors); 
